com.application.tagging

Class RequestTagApplication

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.application.tagging.RequestTagApplication

  • @GroupSequence(value={First.class,RequestTagApplication.class,Second.class})
public class RequestTagApplication
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrapper class on the information needed to specify a pairing of Tag and SkillLevel. Contains data on an existent Tag, an existent SkillLevel, and bounding information for the application.
    Author:
    Tim Schommer
